And then again there will always be some of us who just like to make big trains in densely populated dungeons for the fun of it. I tried making huge trains in permafrost and mistmoore, but with no one to applaud, what was the point?<br>
<br>
Er, nm that previous paragraph... <p><CENTER>G
MF Virtuoso</CENTER>

